Guidelines for data validation.

- Validate body, query and parameters when applicable.
- Use a validation middleware.
- Do schema validation using zod or ajv.
- If errors exists, return a 400 response with error details, do not forward to the controller.
- When reviewing schema definitions, verify that all properties defined in the schema are actually used in the controller to avoid unnecessary validation overhead and potencial confusion.